		<span>2018年2月16日当时有效</span>
		<div class='ca-card-btn'>立即领取</div>
	</div>
	<div class='ca-card ca04'>
		<div class='ca-card-title'>
			<i class="fa fa-share-alt-square" aria-hidden="true"></i>
			2018.2.16
		</div>
		<h3>登山经验分享</h2>
		<div class='ca-card-view' style="background-image:url(./img/rec03.jpg)"></div>
		<p>讲师：张松</p>
